1. Modify the Option Byte you want to modify in the "set_csa.850" file and save
2. Compile the project and connect the target
3.1. Enter "target FLASHEXTRA config1 on" in the 850eserv2 console
3.2. Enter "target FLASHEXTRA security1 on" in the 850eserv2 console
4. Enter "target FLASHEXTRA" to check whether to enable access to the Option Byte area (optional)
5. Click Download to download the program, and the option Byte flashing has been completed after downloading